OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCanada challenges          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcompensation order for     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Findigenous children        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canada says it will appeal against a   
OL,6, court order to pay billions of dollars 
OL,7, to compensate indigenous children who  
OL,8, went through the child welfare system. 
OL,10,FLast month, a top court upheld a 2016  
OL,11,Fruling that the government underfunded 
OL,12,FFirst Nations services compared with   
OL,13,Fthose for non-indigenous children.     
OL,15,FIt ordered C$40,000 ($31,350; #23,340) 
OL,16,Fpayouts to each child forced from home 
OL,17,Finto the on-reserve welfare system.    
OL,19,FThe case has been a source of tension  
OL,20,Fbetween tribes and the government.     
